{"tid":1115753,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"仲記唔記得高登神作《男人唔可以窮》？","createTime":"2019-04-19T12:03:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T03:35:44.000Z","uid":227650,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ae92ab4b6d4800b06a69acf8fc2dd9f1e0da56f1","tid":1115753,"uid":227650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T12:03:06.000Z","msg":"可能係高登最正嘅一個故事 ，係高登會員薛可正嘅出品。呢個故事帶嚟好多共鳴，尤其是香港呢個咁講錢嘅地方，所以呢個故事理所當然咁非常受歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n呢個故仔影響力極大，去到2014年出埋電影《男人唔可以窮》，我記得主要角色有:黃宗澤飾演薛可正、陳偉霆飾演薛可勇、stephy鄧麗欣飾演張以娜、廖啟智飾演薛天來等等。<br />\n<br />\nBtw,擺低故事嘅幾條link <br />\n<br />\nPart1:<a href=\"http://forum7.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=4105908&amp;highlight_id=367378\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum7.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D4105908%26highlight_id%3D367378&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=8dea1a73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://forum7.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=4105908&amp;highlight_id=367378</a><br />\n<br />\nPart2:<a href=\"http://forum7.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=4116449&amp;highlight_id=367378\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum7.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D4116449%26highlight_id%3D367378&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=5be16ede\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://forum7.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=4116449&amp;highlight_id=367378</a><br />\n<br />\nPart3:<a href=\"http://forum7.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=4128643&amp;highlight_id=367378\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum7.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D4128643%26highlight_id%3D367378&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=baf75f9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://forum7.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=4128643&amp;highlight_id=367378</a><br />\n<br />\nPart4:<a href=\"http://forum7.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=4141467&amp;highlight_id=367378\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforu